text: Emilio Massino (16 November 1925 – 17 April 2013) was an Italian sailor who competed in the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Italian male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Italy Category:Sailors at the 1956 Summer Olympics – 12 m2 Sharpie
